data.text:
Rover Dangerfield is the titular main protagonist of the 1991 animated comedy film of the same name. He is a smooth-talking basset hound who was raised by his owner, Connie, a Las Vegas showgirl. But when her jealous boyfriend, Rocky throws him over the Hoover Dam, Rover ends up in a farm where he meets a boy named Danny and a beautiful collie named, Daisy.
